      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I've heard some people argue, though, that this idea is kind of a stretch or that it gives too much power to judges to basically make up new rights. How would you respond to those critics in the lesson? Is their view considered a valid legal critique, or is it just an argument against civil rights progress?",
